# Environment Variables Template for Beacon App

Create a `.env.local` file in the project root and copy the following template:

```
# Database
DATABASE_URL=

# Azure AD SSO
AZURE_AD_CLIENT_ID=
AZURE_AD_CLIENT_SECRET=
AZURE_AD_TENANT_ID=
NEXTAUTH_URL=
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=

# Email Services
SENDGRID_API_KEY=
AZURE_COMMUNICATION_CONNECTION_STRING=

# AI Providers
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# Other
MEILISEARCH_API_KEY=
AZURE_STORAGE_CONNECTION_STRING=
```

> Fill in the values as appropriate for your environment. Never commit secrets to version control.
